{room=188,  	title="The Tailor\'s shop", 	verbose="A few tailors dummy\'s lie around the place but someone seems to have used them for sword practice and consequently there are not really any pieces large enough to take. Apart from this the shop is quite bare except for large quantities of plaster which have fallen from the ceiling. West leads through a doorway into the street.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e="You walk into something solid.", 	w=161, 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You walk into something solid.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o=161, 	u="You can\'t go that way.", 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
