{room=239,  	title="In the realm of hopeless dreams", 	verbose="You are standing on a wire mesh floor through which you can see an imposing array of whining, humming and bleeping machinery. Directly below you there is a large black metal box labelled \'Information Membrane Generator No. 103858sc-R\' from which an uncountable number of multicoloured cables reach up through the floor to form a vaguely spherical shape around you.", 	n="Even though it does sound the same.", 	s="Begin a word ending with H. The last letter minus", 	e="Or you may wind up in trouble", 	w="Is completely unaffected by any economic", 	ne="With a flamboyant wooden legged man", 	nw="From the sun. What would stop it having half that wingspan", 	se="Your view", 	sw="When outgrabeing took place", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o=235, 	u="Take the third letter of the 2nd word.", 	d="Now take the two penultimate letters to get a clue to"},
