{room=260,  	title="Store Cave", 	verbose="This small cave looks as though it was used to store things, judging by the stone shelves jutting from the south wall.  Unfortunately these shelves have long since had their contents removed. A narrow archway leads north back into the low cave.", 	n=254, 	s="The rock isn\'t quite thin enough to be walked through.", 	e="The rock isn\'t quite thin enough to be walked through.", 	w="The rock isn\'t quite thin enough to be walked through.", 	ne="The rock isn\'t quite thin enough to be walked through.", 	nw="There appears to be a wall in the way.", 	se="There appears to be a wall in the way.", 	sw="There appears to be a wall in the way.", 	i="The rock isn\'t quite thin enough to be walked through.", 	o=254, 	u="Sorry. No levitating on these premises.", 	d="You are standing on solid rock. Very solid."},
{room=261,  	title="Huge cavern", 	verbose="You find yourself in a vast rock cavern. Although you are unable to locate any source of light you find you are able to see quite easilly by virtue of a soft glow which seems to eminate from the very walls themselves. You get the impression that this must be a place highly charged with magic. The bronze gate leads westwards into daylight. You also notice a large exit in the north wall and smaller ones leading east and northeast.", 	n=244, 	s="The rock isn\'t quite thin enough to be walked through.", 	e=242, 	w=241, 	ne=248, 	nw="The rock isn\'t quite thin enough to be walked through.", 	se="The rock isn\'t quite thin enough to be walked through.", 	sw="The rock isn\'t quite thin enough to be walked through.", 	i=244, 	o=241, 	u="Sorry. No levitating on these premises.", 	d="You are standing on solid rock. Very solid."},
