{room=273,  	title="The end of a tunnel.", 	verbose="You are at the end of a long, cool tunnel leading east. There is a light breeze coming from that direction. There is a faint glimmer of light above your head and you can just make out a small hole in the ceiling.", 	n="You blunder into a cold, hard wall.", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e=274, 	w="You walk into something solid.", 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="You blunder into a cold, hard wall.", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i=274, 	o=272, 	u=272, 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
