{room=414,  	title="North of the drawbridge", 	verbose="You are stood on the bank of a wide, deep moat which encircles a magnificent stone castle to your east. A few trees grow around you, somewhat thicker to the North and West although passage in those directions should be possible. To the south is the approach to the castle drawbridge.", 	n=415, 	s=6, 	e=12, 	w="Something in the water snaps at you - you retreat hastily.", 	ne=13, 	nw=415, 	se=11, 	sw="Something in the water snaps at you - you retreat hastily.", 	i=415, 	o=6, 	u="Something green and evil slithers towards you...you back down.", 	d="As you try to burrow a snake hisses at you..you jump up."},
{room=415,  	title="Wood by Moat", 	verbose="The trees grows densely here and you have a definite feeling of being watched. To the west the ground slopes sharply down to a moat, and in it you can see the reflection of a huge stone castle.", 	n=416, 	s=414, 	e=13, 	w="Something in the water snaps at you - you retreat hastily.", 	ne=21, 	nw=416, 	se=12, 	sw="You would only fall in and drown.", 	i=416, 	o=414, 	u="A pair of evil green eyes stare at you. Not good.", 	d="Something in the water snaps at you - you retreat hastily."},
{room=416,  	title="Wood by moat", 	verbose="Tree grow all around here, interspersed with cleared areas where the undergrowth is dotted with stumps bearing the marks of a large axe. To the north you can just discern some sort of path and west the moat continues to curve slowly around the castle.", 	n=417, 	s=415, 	e=21, 	w="Something in the water snaps at you - you retreat hastily.", 	ne=418, 	nw=417, 	se=13, 	sw="Something in the water snaps at you - you retreat hastily.", 	i=415, 	o=415, 	u="Something green and evil slithers towards you...you back down.", 	d="As you try to burrow a snake hisses at you..you jump up."},
{room=417,  	title="Path by woodpile", 	verbose="You are on an old beaten path, deep ruts in the ground indicating the presence of a horse and cart sometime in the past. A large pile of cut wood has been heaped on the south side of the path, at the edge of some woods. On the other side of the path is a deep ditch filled with stagnant water leading into the moat at the end of the path, to your west.\nAcross the moat can be seen a magnificent castle with elegant but overgrown gardens to its north.", 	n="The ditch is filled with hissing water snakes.", 	s=416, 	e=418, 	w="Something in the water snaps at you - you retreat hastily.", 	ne="The ditch is filled with hissing water snakes.", 	nw="The ditch is filled with hissing water snakes.", 	se=418, 	sw=416, 	i=416, 	o=418, 	u="The trees are too slender to take your weight.", 	d="Something in the undergrowth stings you nastily."},
{room=418,  	title="Fork in path", 	verbose="A path from the south winds through some woods and forks sharply here, curving around to both the northeast and northwest. Looking along it to the west you can see where the path ends at the banks of a moat, while east the path is somewhat muddy and leads into a dank and misty marsh. North of the path a ditch runs parallel with it, running between the moat and the marsh.", 	n="The ditch is filled with hissing water snakes.", 	s=21, 	e=419, 	w=417, 	ne=419, 	nw=417, 	se=40, 	sw=416, 	i=416, 	o=21, 	u="Think you\'re a bird?", 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
{room=419,  	title="Misty path", 	verbose="You are on a muddy stretch of east/west path, the air around you cold and damp, and smelling faintly of marsh gas. Mist drifts about aimlessly, thicker to the east and obscuring your vision. A deep ditch, filled with stagnant water, blocks passage north.", 	n="The ditch is filled with hissing water snakes.", 	s=40, 	e=16, 	w=418, 	ne="Something evil lurks in the mist there, slavering crazily...", 	nw="The ditch is filled with hissing water snakes.", 	se=16, 	sw=418, 	i=40, 	o=418, 	u="You can\'t climb up here.", 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
