{room=495,  	title="Grand Banqueting Hall.", 	verbose="The calcified food is still on the table.  Twenty giant candle sticks still stand on the massive refectory table. The table is set with magnificent antique silver and Blue Willow china. But no tablecloth.  Down the middle of this highly polished table stands and army of catsup bottles and pickle jars with the labels on. thats the way the Mayor liked it. There is one freshly laid place with a clean plate.  Doors are North, South and West.", 	n=492, 	s=498, 	e="You walk into something solid.", 	w=500, 	ne="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	nw="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	se="You walk into something solid.", 	sw=499, 	i="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	o=492, 	u="You can\'t go that way.", 	d="There\'s no entrance there!"},
