{room=650,  	title="Dusty Corridor", 	verbose="When the King began his long descent into madness, this area of the castle was one of the first to be abandoned.  Consequently the dust and decay is more prevalent here than in any other part of the decrepit building.  The corridor runs a little further south, while two corridors intersect to the north.", 	n=73, 	s=654, 	e=651, 	w="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i=651, 	o=73, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=651,  	title="Chapel", 	verbose="Long ago stripped by looters, the castle chapel is distinguishable only by its large stone altar and the wooden crucifix suspended from the ceiling.  What chairs and furniture there are in the room that haven\'t been destroyed, look far too riddled with woodworm to be usable.  Off to the south side of the chapel is a small cupboard-like room which was, presumably, once the confessional.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s=653, 	e=652, 	w=650, 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i=653, 	o=650, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=652,  	title="Behind the Altar", 	verbose="Something, probably a rat, scuttles away into the shadows as you squeeze behind the altar.  Quite a draught blows through the chinks in the rough-hewn stone wall.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	w=651, 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	o=651, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=653,  	title="Confessional", 	verbose="This is where the King, the court and the castle staff would come to confess their sins and to be shriven.  The tiny room contains nothing more than a chair for the priest, now without a seat, and a kneeling stool for the penitent.  The door swings drunkenly on one hinge, which looks as if it might disintegrate at any moment.", 	n=651, 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	w="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	o=651, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way "},
{room=654,  	title="Dusty Corridor", 	verbose="The dust here is so thick that you can see tracks marking the passage of rats as the scavenge for food in the desolate place.  Splinters of wood attached to huge iron hinges are the only remnants of the door in the east wall, while, flanked on either side by mildewed and rotting shreds of tapestry, the door to the west looks to be very secure.", 	n=650, 	s=658, 	e=655, 	w=656, 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i=655, 	o=650, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=655,  	title="Priest\'s Room", 	verbose="This sparsely furnished room was once inhabited by the resident priest.  However the holy man has long since abandoned this sorry place, and the room looks and smells as if it is now occupied by something unpleasant.  The room is a shambles, but a small cupboard against the far wall appears to be relatively intact.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	w=654, 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	o=654, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=656,  	title="Library", 	verbose="Shreds of paper and half-chewed books in a pile on the floor, are almost all that is left of this once magnificent library.  On each wall, empty shelves stand mute testimony to the knowledge that once accumulated here.  Squinting upwards, you perceive that some volumes may still lie intact on the upper floor.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e=654, 	w="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i=657, 	o=654, 	u=657, 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=657,  	title="Room of Rare Books", 	verbose="The upper reaches of the library were once given over to the more esoteric and expensive tomes.  One or two intact books survive, huddling together in little clusters on the bare shelves, but there would appear to be little of interest.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	w="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	o=656, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d=656},
{room=658,  	title="Dusty Corridor", 	verbose="Curiously enough, this part of the corridor is littered with dried leaves.  A very slight breeze issues from the archway to the east, carrying with it the scent of woodland.", 	n=654, 	s=659, 	e=663, 	w="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i=659, 	o=654, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=659,  	title="Junction", 	verbose="The dusty corridor ends here, with a choice of two smaller, dingier passages to choose from, running east and west.  There is very little to choose between the two, except for the peculiar smell which emanates from the east.", 	n=658, 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e=660, 	w=666, 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i=660, 	o=658, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=660,  	title="Short Passage", 	verbose="There are no windows in this passage, making it very hard to see what lies ahead of you.  The smell to the east, however, is getting stronger as you proceed in that direction.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e=661, 	w=659, 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i=661, 	o=659, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=661,  	title="Castle Apothecary", 	verbose="The light, although scant, is almost blinding after the dark corridor.  As your sight returns you become aware the you have found the workroom of the Court Apothecary.  Charged with the welbeing of the King and all the inhabitants of the castle, the apothecary would have conducted his often unpleasant duties here.  The smell is now almost overpowering, carries with it the odour of chemicals and death.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	w=660, 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw=662, 	i=662, 	o=660, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=662,  	title="Castle Apothecary\'s storeroom", 	verbose="You hastely plug your nose, but still the reek of chemicals and decaying animal and vegetable matter is enough to make you feel faint You wonder how many of the apothecary\'s patients\' illnesses derived from the noxious odours that must have constantly issued from this store", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	w="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	ne=661, 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	o=661, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=663,  	title="Balcony", 	verbose="This east-facing balcony\'s only furniture is a stone seat, from where the sunrise could be observerd by those so inclined.  Both seat and balcony have decayed to such a degree that every footstep is potentially hazardous, even fatal...", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	w=658, 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	o=658, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=664,  	title="Maids\' Room", 	verbose="This small room, containing the ruins of two beds, once housed two of the castle\'s more favoured maids.  Looking at the meagre furnishings, you wonder what kind of squalor was the lot of the less well-off servants.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s=666, 	e="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	w="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	o=666, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=665,  	title="Butler\'s Room", 	verbose="Below the Chamberlain, the Butler was the chief servant of the castle, and this small room shows traces of an elegant past.  From the open wardrobe in one corner, drifts the smell of heavily mildewed cloth, while hanging on the wall next to it, a crazed and speckled mirror reflects the room in strange ways, giving it an almost hellish cast.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e=666, 	w="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	o=666, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=666,  	title="Servants\' Quarters", 	verbose="This cramped passageway leads to the quarters of the higher-ranking castle servants.  A faint noxious smell can still be detected from the east, and you wonder how anyone could have lived in such conditions.", 	n=664, 	s=667, 	e=659, 	w=665, 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i=665, 	o=659, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=667,  	title="Cook\'s Room", 	verbose="In happier days, the Mistress of the Kitchens once resided here.  She ran away with the Butler when things started to get bad, but an apron, mildewed and yellowed with age, hangs on one wall as mute testimony to her passage.", 	n=666, 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	w="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	o=666, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
