{room=750,  	title="Large cavern.", 	verbose="You are in the middle of the cavern, surrounded by impressive stalagmites and stalactites. There is a  passageway leading into the north wall of the cavern, passing between two extra large stalagmites that seem to have formed into a vaguely canine shape.", 	n=751, 	s="You can\'t go that way.", 	e=749, 	w=748, 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i=749, 	o=751, 	u="You must be bats!", 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
{room=751,  	title="Small tunnel.", 	verbose="This is a fairly small tunnel leading north. The floor is covered with a worn but still soft carpet and the walls have been well polished.  A heavy door stands open at the north end of the tunnel. A sign on the door says \'Hermit\'s Hovel - trespassers will be cooked.\'", 	n=752, 	s=750, 	e="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	w="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	ne="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	nw="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	se="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	sw="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	i=752, 	o=750, 	u="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=752,  	title="Hermit\'s Kitchen.", 	verbose="This is a small but well equipped kitchen, spotlessly clean. There is a pot bubbling away on the stove and a delightful aroma fills the air.  Looking in the pot all you can tell is that it contains a stew of some kind. While wondering what could possibly be found down here to make a stew from you rememeber the leech pool and decide you are not really very interested.", 	n="You blunder into a cold, hard wall.", 	s=751, 	e=753, 	w=754, 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i=754, 	o=751, 	u="You must be bats!", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=753,  	title="Hermit\'s Bathroom.", 	verbose="There is a lot of steam in here, and the barely visible bath is full of lovely hot water with bubbles too ! Floating among the bubbles you can see a bright yellow rubber duck and a model boat.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	w=752, 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o=752, 	u="You must be bats!", 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
{room=754,  	title="Hermit\'s Hallway.", 	verbose="The hall leads off to the north-east through a long passage lined with portraits and pot ducks. The faces depicted in the portraits all have very long beards and don\'t seem at all friendly. The ducks, while clean shaven, don\'t have very friendly expressions either.", 	n="You can\'t go that way.", 	s="You blunder into a cold, hard wall.", 	e=752, 	w="You blunder into a cold, hard wall.", 	ne=755, 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i=755, 	o=752, 	u="You must be bats!", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=755,  	title="Hermit\'s Living room.", 	verbose="This room contains a comfy sofa and a rocking chair, both facing a strange box with a glass front. On top of the box there is an empty vase, a photograph and a lamp. In the north wall there is a large fireplace with coal piled up in it. The fire is not lit however.", 	n=758, 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e=757, 	w=756, 	ne=761, 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw=754, 	i="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	o=754, 	u="You must be bats!", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=756,  	title="Hermit\'s Bedroom.", 	verbose="This is a low lit, cosy little room with a well made bed in one corner.  On a small table by the bed there is a glass of water and an opened book. The cover of the book is too faded for you too make out the title.  There is a large wooden wardrobe standing on the floor opposite the bed with some sort of scratch marks on the floor by it.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e=755, 	w="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i=762, 	o=755, 	u="You must be bats!", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=757,  	title="Hermit\'s Study.", 	verbose="A small desk with a reading light on it is against the east wall, under a well stocked book shelf. On the shelf you can make out titles like \'Medition For One\',\'101 Ways To Cook Leeches\',\'Diary of an Arch-Wizard by Ambushbug\' and many more.", 	n="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	s="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	e="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	w=755, 	ne="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	nw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	se="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	sw="Walking through walls was never your strong point", 	i="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	o=755, 	u="You must be bats!", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=758,  	title="In the Hermit\'s fireplace.", 	verbose="You are standing on a pile of coal in the fireplace! I wouldn\'t stay here too long if I were you, someone might want to relax by a real fire!", 	n="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	s=755, 	e="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	w="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	ne="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	nw="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	se="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	sw="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	i=755, 	o=759, 	u=759, 	d="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress."},
{room=759,  	title="Halfway up the Hermit\'s chimney.", 	verbose="You are halfway up the chimney surrounded by soot. And what a lot of soot there is too...  If you go up you might just be able to squeeze past a tight turn in the chimney, but I\'m not going to guarantee anything.", 	n="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	s="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	e="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	w="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	ne="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	nw="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	se="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	sw="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	i=758, 	o=760, 	u=760, 	d=758},
{room=760,  	title="Near top of Hermit\'s chimney.", 	verbose="You can see light from above and hear the sounds of happy birds chirping to each other. The chimney carries on down but there is a tight turn and I don\'t think you\'d fit past it.", 	n="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	s="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	e="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	w="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	ne="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	nw="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	se="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	sw="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	i="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	o=145, 	u=145, 	d="The gap\'s too small for you to fit through."},
{room=761,  	title="Hermit\'s Coal hole.", 	verbose="There is a lot of coal piled up in this little room, mostly arranged into neat piles along the north wall though one or two naughty lumps have rolled out into the middle of the floor.  High out of reach in the north wall there is a hole through which daylight is shining. The hole is far to small to climb out of though, even if you could get up to it.", 	n="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	s="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	e="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	w="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	ne="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	nw="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	se="You get covered in charcoal, but make no progress.", 	sw=755, 	i="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	o=755, 	u="You must be bats!", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=762,  	title="Inside Hermit\'s wardrobe.", 	verbose="This wardrobe contains many, neatly hung up clothes but it is very unlikely that any of them are in your size so leave them where they are.", 	n="That\'s not the way out.", 	s="That\'s not the way out.", 	e="That\'s not the way out.", 	w="That\'s not the way out.", 	ne="That\'s not the way out.", 	nw="That\'s not the way out.", 	se="That\'s not the way out.", 	sw="That\'s not the way out.", 	i="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way", 	o=756, 	u="You must be bats!", 	d="A mysterious force prevents you moving that way"},
{room=763,  	title="Dining room.", 	verbose="You are at the south end of a long dining room which contains a large table carved out of a strange dark wood. The table is completely bare except for some peculiar brown stains near it\'s centre. Above the table there is an elabourate chandelier, now a home for a multitude of large, extremely hairy, spiders, some of which are curiously observing you.", 	n=764, 	s="The candles flicker briefly as you bump into the wall.", 	e=725, 	w="The candles flicker briefly as you bump into the wall.", 	ne="The candles flicker briefly as you bump into the wall.", 	nw="The candles flicker briefly as you bump into the wall.", 	se="The candles flicker briefly as you bump into the wall.", 	sw="The candles flicker briefly as you bump into the wall.", 	i=764, 	o=725, 	u="The ceiling is far too high for you to reach.", 	d="The floor is in the way."},
{room=764,  	title="Dining room.", 	verbose="You are at the north end of a long dining room, standing next to an empty drinks cabinet. There is a large table to the south and a small doorway leading northeast.", 	n="The candles flicker briefly as you bump into the wall.", 	s=763, 	e=726, 	w="The candles flicker briefly as you bump into the wall.", 	ne=765, 	nw="The candles flicker briefly as you bump into the wall.", 	se="The candles flicker briefly as you bump into the wall.", 	sw="The candles flicker briefly as you bump into the wall.", 	i=763, 	o=726, 	u="The ceiling is far too high for you to reach.", 	d="The floor is in the way."},
{room=765,  	title="Dusty Kitchen.", 	verbose="This is the kitchen and has obviously not been used for a long time.  The bone dry sink is full of a strange brown dust and the cupboards and stove are covered with cobwebs. There is a dark forbidding room down some steps to the east, a small pantry to the west and doorways leading south and southwest.  The north wall is obscured by a formless grey fog...", 	n=723, 	s=726, 	e=731, 	w=766, 	ne="You recoil from the touch of cobwebs against your skin.", 	nw="You recoil from the touch of cobwebs against your skin.", 	se="You recoil from the touch of cobwebs against your skin.", 	sw=764, 	i=764, 	o=726, 	u="The ceiling is far too high for you to reach.", 	d=731},
