{room=841,  	title="Information Centre", 	verbose="In this, the Information Centre, doors lead off in all directions, including the west where there is a forbidding portal marked \"To the Game\". A sign hanging overhead reads \"Stuck? Type HELP! And if you get lost, keep going OUT.\" The north door is marked \"Scripting Rules\" while the one to the south is marked \"Instructions\". There is also a sturdy door to the east, marked \"Life and Death in the Land\", and a hole leading downwards with a sign \"Mortal Guidelines\". ", 	n=870, 	s=871, 	e=861, 	w=4, 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se=584, 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i=846, 	o=4, 	u=584, 	d=843},
{room=842,  	title="The Reception Area", 	verbose="You have arrived in a warm, brightly lit cavern with smooth, featureless rock walls and no way out save a tunnel to the east. Not altogether sure how you got here or what to do next, you notice a sign hanging from the ceiling. The script is unfamiliar, almost gothic, yet you can still make out the writing:\n\"Welcome to the Land of Shades! Your first steps in this Land will be aided greatly by study of the Information Centre, which can be entered by travelling east from here.\"", 	n="You can\'t go that way.", 	s="You can\'t go that way.", 	e=841, 	w="You can\'t go that way.", 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o=841, 	u="You can\'t go that way.", 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
{room=843,  	title="Mortal Guidelines", 	verbose="Here are a few guidelines that allow you to avoid having the wraith of the immortals rain down upon you!\n\n1) No swearing, especially in shouts\n2) Play each of your personna\'s seperately, i.e. Do not use a lower level personna to collect treasure for one of your higher level players\n3) If attacking another player please do not use level difference to your advantage, ie don\'t use a necro to attack a mystical (unless of course you have been provoked!!!)\n\nMore East, Out for Info Centre", 	n=841, 	s=841, 	e=844, 	w=841, 	ne=841, 	nw=841, 	se=841, 	sw=841, 	i=841, 	o=841, 	u=841, 	d=841},
{room=844,  	title="Mortal Guidelines 2", 	verbose="4) Low stamming, ie attacking a player when they are not on full stamina, although not against the rules is considered bad karma, so do it at your own risk!\n\nThats about it, if you follow these guidelines then you will be ok, break them and prepare for the wraith of the immortals to rain down upon you!!\n\nOut for Info Centre", 	n=841, 	s=841, 	e=841, 	w=841, 	ne=841, 	nw=841, 	se=841, 	sw=841, 	i=841, 	o=841, 	u=841, 	d=841},
{room=845,  	title="The Shades Chronicles", 	verbose="Welcome to Shades\nJust a small update this one, one change that discourages certain behaviour with the brass key.... Now you cannot be a pacifist when you score reaches that of Enchanter/ess or above. On your your first save or quit after reach that level you will revert to fighter mode. Also you can now switch back to a fighter with no score penalty with MODE FIGHTER CONFIRM.\nRemember MODE PACIFIST CONFIRM will always reset your score to zero! Peri.\n-- South for Info Centre -- ", 	n="You can\'t go that way.", 	s=841, 	e="You can\'t go that way.", 	w="You can\'t go that way.", 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o=841, 	u="You can\'t go that way.", 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
{room=846,  	title="Shades Update 27Dec96", 	verbose="A couple of little tweaks have been performed to make the black tower a little more accessable, you wont always have to trek so far to find that lost chord, and if you wish to do without the blue drink behaves somewhat differently now.  Finally, you no longer need two people to ring those bells, but you will have to be quick!\n-- Old News North, or OUT to the information centre -- ", 	n=845, 	s=841, 	e="You can\'t go that way.", 	w="You can\'t go that way.", 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i=845, 	o=841, 	u="You can\'t go that way.", 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
