{room=1060, title="Stood behind you licking your ear!", 	verbose="You are stood in what appears to be the lair of a madman. On the walls are several portraits of a beautiful woman, as you look closely at these you can just make out the name \'Rhiannon\'.  Removing the dust you can also make out an inscription which says \'Rhiannon rings like a bell in the night\'\nZeon the Mipselt Arch-Wizard is sat in a chair in the corner\n...or at least you think he is!", 	n=1053, 	s="You can\'t go that way.", 	e="You can\'t go that way.", 	w="You can\'t go that way.", 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o=581, 	u=99, 	d=1075},
{room=1061, title="Total Darkness", 	verbose="The room is so dark you cannot see a thing! Suddenly, from out of nowhere, you hear a faint >click<\nIn an instant you notice that the room was not empty all along, Everything glows under an UltraViolet light! There is a bright orange table in the center of the room with a couple of empty green beer glasses apon it, and a bright (almost too bright) sofa to one side. In this strange light, you realise your shoulders are covered in dandruff! ", 	n=1061, 	s=1061, 	e=1061, 	w=1061, 	ne=1061, 	nw=1061, 	se=1061, 	sw=1061, 	i=1061, 	o=1061, 	u=582, 	d=581},
{room=1062, title="A cosy but untidy and cluttered place", 	verbose="Despite its cluttered appearance two items stand out Firstly there is a pristine Mouze basket clearly never used Secondly a bookcase with hundreds of well thumbed paperbacks, by looking you can guess that some of my favourite authors are John Fowles and John Irving and Ian MacEwan. You feel that this room is rarely used for more than convenience and relax", 	n="You can\'t go that way.", 	s="You can\'t go that way.", 	e="You can\'t go that way.", 	w="You can\'t go that way.", 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o="You can\'t go that way.", 	u="You can\'t go that way.", 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
