{room=1066, title="Ynys Witrin", 	verbose="This is the home of the wizard, Merlin. It\'s full of the bric-a-brac of a life of travel and adventure.  Over the chair is a well-worn wizard\'s robe in what appear to be West Ham colours. On the floor, there\'s a comfy looking hat. The room\'s most striking feature is an iridescent white statue of Michelangelo\'s David. \"Blimey!\" you think as you help yourself to a Calvados.", 	n="You can\'t go that way.", 	s="You can\'t go that way.", 	e="You can\'t go that way.", 	w="You can\'t go that way.", 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o="You can\'t go that way.", 	u="You can\'t go that way.", 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
{room=1067, title="Deckard\'s Room of Lucidity", 	verbose="You look up into a swirl of heavy darkness, your eyes fixate on wonderous shapes...shapes that resemble genetic strands, they glow vibrantly releasing a powerful glow of every colour in the spectrum...  the colour pushes a warmth you could have never imagined...  your heart races to an infinitive state, energy pulsates around you..  swirling into a steady twist of peace....  you have found the room of lucidity...and it likes you...\nThe only exit is out leading to Outside the \"Shalking Toppe\" Pub.", 	n="You can\'t go that way.", 	s="You can\'t go that way.", 	e="You can\'t go that way.", 	w="You can\'t go that way.", 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o=581, 	u=1067, 	d="You can\'t go that way. "},
{room=1068, title="Wired\'s Lounge", 	verbose="You are in a strange but comfortable room, with plenty of soft chairs and a small round table. There are numerous parts of old PC\'s and telecomms equipment strewn on a bench on the far wall. There is ambient music playing on a battered Sony CD player.  There is a fridge in one corner which has a sign saying Help Yourself, swinging from a magnet Every so often a modem noise interrupts the music...  Oh, and if Wired is here, he is probably asleep.", 	n=10, 	s=1, 	e=1067, 	w=1069, 	ne=150, 	nw=130, 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o=581, 	u=64, 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
{room=1069, title="This is where Lingus lives", 	verbose="This is a very strange place indeed . . .\nThere are trees growing all around you Bottles containing potions and strong drink, and ready-to-eat meals hang from the branches. There is a large comfortable bed in front of you. A log fire is burning in a stone hearth next to a large leather sofa A large vase of flowers is on the mantlepiece To the east you hear the sound of someone tapping a keyboard.  The sound of mortals chattering comes from the south", 	n=320, 	s=581, 	e=1068, 	w="You can\'t go that way.", 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i=1069, 	o=1069, 	u="You can\'t go that way.", 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
{room=1070, title="Treasure Hunt Info and Rules", 	verbose="The hunt will take place on the QUIZ game and will last for 45 minutes or until all treasure has been collected, whichever comes first.  One piece of treasure will be placed at a random location in the game and the first person to get the treasure and put it in the fountain in the formal gardens will score the points for that treasure.  This will be repeated for another piece of treasure until the game is over.\nMORE NORTH", 	n=1071, 	s="You can\'t go that way.", 	e="You can\'t go that way.", 	w="You can\'t go that way.", 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o="You can\'t go that way.", 	u="You can\'t go that way.", 	d=581},
{room=1071, title="Treasure Hunt Info and Rules", 	verbose="At the end of the game each player will have a tally of the number of pieces of treasure they have managed to put in the pond and will be awarded with an additional 100 points per item which will be added to the score of the personna they are playing with.  In addition 1000, 500 and 200 points will also be awarded for 1st, 2nd and 3rd place.  Fighting will be turned off during the game so there will be NO possibility of being attacked by either a mobile or player\nMORE NORTH - BACK SOUTH", 	n=1072, 	s=1070, 	e="You can\'t go that way.", 	w="You can\'t go that way.", 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o="You can\'t go that way.", 	u="You can\'t go that way.", 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
