{room=1074, title="Zinny\'s Retreat", 	verbose="The room has changed yet again, a large open fireplace with marble hearth has merged with the shimmering yet translucent walls to form a focal point. The large sofa remains, wrapping itself around your body as you sit. The room has a warm and homely feel, yet you sense you are not alone. An enormous bed invites you through the shimmering partition wall, offering untold pleasures. Conjure up your wildest dreams and they may just come true.", 	n=581, 	s="You can\'t go that way.", 	e="You can\'t go that way.", 	w="You can\'t go that way.", 	ne="You can\'t go that way.", 	nw="You can\'t go that way.", 	se="You can\'t go that way.", 	sw="You can\'t go that way.", 	i="You can\'t go that way.", 	o=581, 	u=585, 	d="You can\'t go that way."},
